<div class="main">
  <div class="professional-info-container">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">運営情報</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">About College Spark</p>
        <div class="hero-divider"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Overview -->
    <section class="section-wrapper">
      <div class="section-content overview-section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>サービス概要</h2>
          <p class="section-description">College Sparkは、海外大学進学を検討する学生・保護者の皆様に、信頼性の高い大学情報を提供する情報プラットフォームです。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-grid">
          <div class="overview-card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>信頼性の高いデータ</h3>
            <p>U.S. Department of Education College Scorecardなど公的機関のデータに基づいた正確な情報を提供</p>
          </div>

          <div class="overview-card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>実体験に基づく情報</h3>
            <p>アメリカ大学卒業者による実際の留学経験を基にした信頼できる情報提供</p>
          </div>

          <div class="overview-card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M3 14h18m-9-4v8m-7 0h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>完全中立・非営利</h3>
            <p>特定大学からの報酬や広告収入は一切なし。純粋な情報提供のみを目的とした運営</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founder Profile -->
    <section class="section-wrapper founder-section-bg">
      <div class="section-content">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>運営者プロフィール</h2>
          <p class="section-description">Founder Profile</p>
        </div>

        <div class="founder-profile">
          <div class="founder-image-container">
            <%= image_tag 'profile-graduation.jpg', class: 'founder-image', alt: '運営者' %>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-details">
            <div class="founder-name">
              <h3>College Spark 運営者</h3>
              <p class="founder-title">Founder & Developer</p>
            </div>

            <div class="credentials-list">
              <div class="credential-item">
                <div class="credential-icon">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-content">
                  <h4>学歴</h4>
                  <p>アメリカ・オハイオ州の大学卒業（2024年）</p>
                  <p class="credential-detail">専攻：生物学（Biology）</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="credential-item">
                <div class="credential-icon">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 713.138-3.138z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-content">
                  <h4>学業実績</h4>
                  <p>Dean's List 掲載 / Honor Society 会員</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="credential-item">
                <div class="credential-icon">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-content">
                  <h4>リーダーシップ経験</h4>
                  <p>Japanese Student Organization 会長</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="credential-item">
                <div class="credential-icon">
                  <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m8 0h4m-4 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h8z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-content">
                  <h4>職歴</h4>
                  <p>現地インターンシップ 3ヶ月</p>
                  <p class="credential-detail">現在：IT企業 ソフトウェアエンジニア</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Statement -->
    <section class="section-wrapper">
      <div class="section-content mission-section">
        <div class="mission-content">
          <div class="mission-icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>ミッション</h2>
          <p>
            College Sparkは、海外大学進学を目指す全ての学生が、正確で信頼できる情報に基づいて最適な大学選択ができる環境を提供します。
            実体験に基づく知見と、公的機関の客観的データを組み合わせることで、皆様の人生を変える決断をサポートします。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <section class="section-wrapper disclaimer-section-bg">
      <div class="section-content">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>重要事項</h2>
          <p class="section-description">Important Notice</p>
        </div>

        <div class="disclaimer-grid">
          <div class="disclaimer-card">
            <div class="disclaimer-number">01</div>
            <h3>非営利運営</h3>
            <p>本サイトは完全に非営利で運営されています。広告収入や特定大学からの報酬は一切受け取っておりません。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="disclaimer-card">
            <div class="disclaimer-number">02</div>
            <h3>中立的立場</h3>
            <p>特定の大学への進学を促すものではありません。客観的データに基づいた情報提供に徹しています。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="disclaimer-card">
            <div class="disclaimer-number">03</div>
            <h3>情報の利用</h3>
            <p>提供情報は参考資料です。最終的な決定は、ご自身の状況を総合的に考慮して行ってください。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tech Stack -->
    <section class="section-wrapper">
      <div class="section-content tech-section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>技術スタック</h2>
          <p class="section-description">Technology Stack</p>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-grid">
          <div class="tech-category">
            <h3>Backend</h3>
            <p>Ruby on Rails</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-category">
            <h3>Frontend</h3>
            <p>HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-category">
            <h3>Database</h3>
            <p>SQLite</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-category">
            <h3>Data Source</h3>
            <p>U.S. Dept. of Education</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <section class="section-wrapper cta-section-bg">
      <div class="section-content cta-section">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>お問い合わせ</h2>
          <p>College Sparkに関するご質問・ご意見は、お問い合わせページよりご連絡ください。</p>
          <p class="cta-message">皆様の海外進学を心より応援しています。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* Container */
  .professional-info-container {
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
    padding: 80px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0.8;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    margin: 30px auto 0;
  }

  /* Section Wrapper */
  .section-wrapper {
    padding: 80px 20px;
  }

  .section-content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Overview Section */
  .overview-section {
    background: #fafafa;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .overview-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .overview-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .card-icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: white;
  }

  .overview-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .overview-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #666;
  }

  /* Founder Section */
  .founder-section-bg {
    background: #f5f5f5;
  }

  .founder-profile {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .founder-image-container {
    position: relative;
  }

  .founder-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .founder-details {
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .founder-name h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .founder-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .credentials-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 25px;
  }

  .credential-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid rgb(240, 177, 61);
  }

  .credential-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(240, 177, 61, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .credential-icon svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: rgb(240, 177, 61);
  }

  .credential-content h4 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .credential-content p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .credential-detail {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #999;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    background: #fafafa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .mission-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 25px;
  }

  .mission-icon svg {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    color: white;
  }

  .mission-content h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .mission-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #555;
  }

  /* Disclaimer Section */
  .disclaimer-section-bg {
    background: #f5f5f5;
  }

  .disclaimer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .disclaimer-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .disclaimer-number {
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(240, 177, 61, 0.1);
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .disclaimer-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .disclaimer-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #666;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Tech Section */
  .tech-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 25px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .tech-category {
    background: #fafafa;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .tech-category:hover {
    border-color: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    background: white;
  }

  .tech-category h3 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .tech-category p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section-bg {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .cta-message {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgb(240, 177, 61);
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .section-wrapper {
      padding: 50px 15px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .founder-profile {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .founder-image-container {
      max-width: 250px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .overview-section {
      padding: 40px 25px;
    }

    .mission-content {
      padding: 40px 25px;
    }

    .credential-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .tech-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .disclaimer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>